19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 301B of Title 44, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving
23 fund for the Oklahoma Military Department to be designated the "Base
24 Infrastructure Needs and Development - Technology Revolving Fund",
